cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI

This paper is about a new training algorithm for deep networks, which improves interpretability of internal representations at the node level. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and social networks (cs.SI), which are also possible categories.
